CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS orders (
  order_id           BIGINT,           -- 6146460123432
  order_number       TEXT,             -- "#1057"
  payment_status     TEXT,             -- "paid"
  order_date         TIMESTAMPTZ,      -- "2024-11-03T20:49:10-05:00"
  subtotal           NUMERIC(10, 2),   -- "324.97"
  total              NUMERIC(10, 2),   -- "338.47"
  currency           TEXT,             -- "EUR"
  discount_code      TEXT,             -- ""
  product_name       TEXT,             -- "Big Brown Bear Boots"
  product_price      NUMERIC(10, 2),   -- "74.99"
  quantity           INTEGER,          -- 3
  shipping_method    TEXT,             -- ""
  shipping_address   TEXT,             -- ""
  notes              TEXT              -- ""
);
